Went for the first time and will definitely be back! This is the quickest hot pot service I've ever experienced. The food was fresh and absolutely delicious. FANTASTIC price for what you get. For example, if there's a lot of oil at the top of your pot, put in ice & scoop it out with a spoon! No more oil in the pot.  The atmosphere is family & group friendly. It was a bit loud at first when we were there but the music drowned out conversations at other tables once it came on later in the night. There's an appetizer and sauce buffet but I think the real treat is in the hot pot menu. [Edit] Their sushi is super fresh and delicious.
